---
title: Lentil Shepherd's Pie with butternut squash topping
description: Lentils replace lamb in this shepherd's pie for a veggie-friendly take on a classic recipe. The creamy butternut squash topping is another unexpected and delicious twist in this healthy, hearty dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220921_R09_W46_IE_IEVV0163-1_KB_Main_high-6693aed9.jpg
